=head1 DESCRIPTION

For a Distillation job, the status details for sub-tasks of the job.
Possible statuses for each sub-task include the following:

=over

=item *

NotStarted

=item *

InProgress

=item *

Completed

=item *

Stopping

=item *

Stopped

=item *

Failed

=back


